      <title>摩根大通领跌银行 前景黯淡 规则胜利在望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/jpmorgan-leads-banks-in-dimming-outlooks-spoiling-win-on-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行在新的资本规定方面从监管机构那里获得了巨大突破 — — 但他们自己的庆祝活动却因对贷款的悲观前景而被破坏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/jpmorgan-leads-banks-in-dimming-outlooks-spoiling-win-on-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 19:07:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
